# Front-End PrivateLink Visual Explainer

Read docs/PRD.md before doing any work. It contains full requirements, scenarios, layout, and tech stack.

## Quick Reference
- Plain HTML/CSS/JS — no frameworks, no build step, no CDN dependencies
- Animated inline SVG + CSS animations for diagrams
- Single page with scenario selector that updates all content in-place
- Three scenarios: Public Path, Wildcard DNS Fwd, Workspace DNS Fwd
- Databricks-specific components (control plane, workspace URL, VPCE service)
- Light Databricks branding (#FF3621 orange, #1B3139 dark, #00A972 green)
- Desktop-optimized (1280px+ viewport)
- GitHub Pages hosting
- Two animation modes: auto-loop and step-through
- Compare mode: side-by-side two-scenario comparison
- PDF export via @media print + export button
- Contextual links to official Databricks PrivateLink docs

See CLAUDE.md for additional context. See docs/PRD.md Section 7.1 for file structure.
